<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Upload Success - SecureFiles</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>File Upload Successful!</h1>
    
    <p>Your file "<strong><%= filename %></strong>" has been uploaded successfully.</p>
    
    <h2>Important Information</h2>
    
    <p><strong>File UUID:</strong></p>
    <pre><%= uuid %></pre>
    
    <p><strong>Current TOTP Code:</strong></p>
    <pre><%= token %></pre>
    
    <p style="color: red;">
        <strong>Important:</strong> Save the UUID to download your file later. 
        The TOTP code changes every 30 seconds. You will need to generate a new code when downloading.
    </p>
    
    <h3>Download Link</h3>
    <p>
        <a href="/download/<%= uuid %>">Click here to download your file</a>
    </p>
    
    <hr>
    
    <p>
        <a href="/">Upload another file</a>
    </p>
</body>
</html>
